  <brief_title>Antioxidant Effect of Aged Garlic Extract</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo Controlled, Crossover Study to Evaluate the Antioxidant Effect of Aged Garlic Extract in Heavy Smokers</official_title>
  <sponsors>
